# Skill Auto-Invocation

When a compound-engineering skill matches the task, use it instead of doing the work ad-hoc. Full skill list: `@plugins/compound-engineering/README.md`

Common routing:
- Committing changes -> `git-commit` or `git-commit-push-pr`
- Reproducing a bug -> `reproduce-bug`
- Resolving PR feedback -> `resolve-pr-feedback`
- Triaging todos -> `todo-triage`
- Building UI components -> `frontend-design`
- Cleaning stale branches -> `git-clean-gone-branches`
